{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775889607998,"sessionID":"ses_284c05ab3ffeBmCKvtfLPbCBtr","part":{"id":"prt_d7b4293cc001dhU9LheS5mOJ4i","messageID":"msg_d7b4284f3001YxIU87tw090FHc","sessionID":"ses_284c05ab3ffeBmCKvtfLPbCBtr","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_5f77f5f23cea4945b2ee9949","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/pkg/tasks.md","content":"# AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) |\n| Module | pkg |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | L |\n| Stage | ST-3 completed |\n\n## Objective\n\n提升 `pkg/router`、`pkg/store` 和 `pkg/picod` 三个模块的单元测试覆盖率，修复现有测试失败，确保代码质量。\n\n## Current Status\n\n### Router\n- Current Coverage: 51.2% (main), 71.4% (blacklist), auth 有失败测试\n- Failed Tests: \n  - `TestJWTConfig_GetSigningKey/base64_encoded_secret_key`\n  - `TestJWTAuthenticator_Validate_Expired`\n  - `TestJWTAuthenticator_Refresh_Expired` (panic)\n\n### Store\n- Current Coverage: 68.9%\n- Status: 所有测试通过\n\n### PicoD\n- Current Coverage: 79.9%\n- Failed Tests:\n  - `TestExecutor_WithTimeout`\n  - `TestPicoD_Integration_FullLifecycle`\n  - `TestPicoD_Integration_Streaming`\n  - `TestPicoD_Integration_Timeout`\n  - `TestPicoD_Integration_EnvironmentVariables`\n  - `TestRunWithStreaming_StdoutStderr`\n\n## Target Coverage\n\n- Router: ≥ 80%\n- Store: ≥ 80%\n- PicoD: ≥ 85%\n\n---\n\n## Atomic Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Router 模块测试修复与增强\n\n#### 1.1 Router Auth 测试修复\n\n- [ ] **TASK-R001**: 修复 `TestJWTConfig_GetSigningKey/base64_encoded_secret_key`\n  - 文件：`pkg/router/auth/config_test.go`\n  - 问题：base64 解码逻辑错误\n  - 验证：测试通过\n\n- [ ] **TASK-R002**: 修复 `TestJWTAuthenticator_Validate_Expired`\n  - 文件：`pkg/router/auth/jwt_test.go`\n  - 问题：过期时间设置问题导致 \"expiration must be positive\" 错误\n  - 验证：测试通过\n\n- [ ] **TASK-R003**: 修复 `TestJWTAuthenticator_Refresh_Expired` panic\n  - 文件：`pkg/router/